(6, 1, '2013-11-20 06:51:52', '2013-11-20 06:51:52', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://localhost/bryanerayner/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 06:51:52', '2013-11-20 06:51:52', '', 2, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?p=6', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(7, 1, '2013-11-20 06:59:01', '2013-11-20 06:59:01', '<p>I provide services in web design &amp; development. I work with teams across the globe and locally to produce quality content.</p>\n\nDecember 2013\n\n\nM\nT\nW\nT\nF\nS\nS\n\n\n\n\n\n<a href="http://localhost/bryanerayner/2013/11/" title="View posts for November 2013">&laquo; Nov</a>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n\n\n\n\n&nbsp;1\n\n\n2345678\n\n\n9101112131415\n\n\n16171819202122\n\n\n23242526272829\n\n\n3031\n&nbsp;\n\n\n', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'services', '', '', '2013-12-03 21:43:35', '2013-12-03 21:43:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(54, 1, '2013-12-03 21:40:00', '2013-12-03 21:40:00', '<h3 class="widget-title">This is My Title</h3>			This is my page.\n\nDecember 2013\n\n\nM\nT\nW\nT\nF\nS\nS\n\n\n\n\n\n<a href="http://localhost/bryanerayner/2013/11/" title="View posts for November 2013">&laquo; Nov</a>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n\n\n\n\n&nbsp;1\n\n\n2345678\n\n\n9101112131415\n\n\n16171819202122\n\n\n23242526272829\n\n\n3031\n&nbsp;\n\n\n', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-03 21:40:00', '2013-12-03 21:40:00', '', 7, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(8, 1, '2013-11-20 06:59:01', '2013-11-20 06:59:01', 'I provide web development services in every spectrum, from user experience to database design. The web provides a unique opportunity to work for almost anyone in the world. It''s been my pleasure to work with great clients, both as a part of a product team, and as an independent contractor. Have something in mind? I hope you''ll find what you''re looking for.', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 06:59:01', '2013-11-20 06:59:01', '', 7, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?p=8', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2013-11-20 07:02:36', '2013-11-20 07:02:36', 'I have experience as a developer as well as a designer. For me, design starts with the user experience, which informs the message and tone of a web product. From that point, content, functionality, and design come together to deliver exactly what your customers are looking for.\r\n\r\nYou may be looking for something specific in your end product. Here''s where my work has taken me so far:\r\n\r\nRich Clientside Experiences\r\n\r\nWeb app development in .NET\r\n\r\nOrganization branding\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Web Development & Design', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'web-development-design', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:02:37', '2013-11-20 07:02:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2013-11-20 07:02:37', '2013-11-20 07:02:37', 'I have experience as a developer as well as a designer. For me, design starts with the user experience, which informs the message and tone of a web product. From that point, content, functionality, and design come together to deliver exactly what your customers are looking for.\r\n\r\nYou may be looking for something specific in your end product. Here''s where my work has taken me so far:\r\n\r\nRich Clientside Experiences\r\n\r\nWeb app development in .NET\r\n\r\nOrganization branding\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Web Development & Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:02:37', '2013-11-20 07:02:37', '', 9, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2013-11-20 07:03:00', '2013-11-20 07:03:00', 'Here''s my best work:', 'Past Projects', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'past-projects', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:03:00', '2013-11-20 07:03:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2013-11-20 07:03:00', '2013-11-20 07:03:00', 'Here''s my best work:', 'Past Projects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:03:00', '2013-11-20 07:03:00', '', 11, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2013-11-20 07:08:36', '2013-11-20 07:08:36', 'Think I''d be a good fit for your product? I''m just as excited as you are to get started.\r\n\r\nIt''s important to me that you understand exactly what you''re getting into before hiring me on a project. To start, let me know what you''re thinking! I''ll be sure to get back to you as soon as I can.', 'Hire Me', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hire-me', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:08:36', '2013-11-20 07:08:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(14, 1, '2013-11-20 07:08:36', '2013-11-20 07:08:36', 'Think I''d be a good fit for your product? I''m just as excited as you are to get started.\r\n\r\nIt''s important to me that you understand exactly what you''re getting into before hiring me on a project. To start, let me know what you''re thinking! I''ll be sure to get back to you as soon as I can.', 'Hire Me', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:08:36', '2013-11-20 07:08:36', '', 13, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(15, 1, '2013-11-20 07:10:14', '2013-11-20 07:10:14', 'Projects are defined in one week sprints - Throughout the project, expect constant communication about important milestones, features, and design issues that need to be addressed. Each project carries it''s own unique schedule, so getting a great design started is vital.', 'My Workflow', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'my-workflow', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:10:14', '2013-11-20 07:10:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?page_id=15', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(16, 1, '2013-11-20 07:10:14', '2013-11-20 07:10:14', 'Projects are defined in one week sprints - Throughout the project, expect constant communication about important milestones, features, and design issues that need to be addressed. Each project carries it''s own unique schedule, so getting a great design started is vital.', 'My Workflow', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:10:14', '2013-11-20 07:10:14', '', 15, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(17, 1, '2013-11-20 07:11:38', '2013-11-20 07:11:38', 'My going rate for small projects is as follows:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nShould you have a project that takes over 2 weeks to complete, a custom pricing plan will be devised based on the feature set and time commitment. I want you to get the best service possible, and am looking forward to hearing about your project!', 'My Rates', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'my-rates', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:11:38', '2013-11-20 07:11:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/?page_id=17', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(18, 1, '2013-11-20 07:11:38', '2013-11-20 07:11:38', 'My going rate for small projects is as follows:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nShould you have a project that takes over 2 weeks to complete, a custom pricing plan will be devised based on the feature set and time commitment. I want you to get the best service possible, and am looking forward to hearing about your project!', 'My Rates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-20 07:11:38', '2013-11-20 07:11:38', '', 17, 'http://localhost/bryanerayner/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
